    Author `GetFileManifestHandler` (NEW) at `src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Handlers/GetFileManifestHandler.cs` implementing the T2 `get_file_manifest(fileId)` tool per architecture ¬ß8.1. Returns the structural manifest for a specific uploaded session file: fileName, pageCount, sections[{name, startPage, endPage}], tables[{name, page}], citations count, language, extractedText{chars, tokens}, classifiedDocType, classifiedConfidence, sha256. Reads from `ChatSession.UploadedFiles[fileId]` populated by the upload pipeline (tasks 066‚Äď074). Implements FR-30 (get_file_manifest row of the 8-tool surface).
