  <role>SPAARKE platform BFF developer. Expert in chat tool-handler authoring + auto-discovered `sprk_analysistool` registration.</role>

  <goal>
    `GetFileManifestHandler` lives at `Services/Ai/Handlers/GetFileManifestHandler.cs` implementing `IToolHandler`. Single `ToolResult` (no streaming, ADR-033). Auto-discovered via `AddToolHandlersFromAssembly`. Returns the ¬ß8.1 manifest shape verbatim. Returns a structured `not_found` payload when `fileId` is not in the session (graceful error per architecture ¬ß9.2). Telemetry: handlerName + sessionId + fileId (deterministic ID ‚ÄĒ tier-1 safe per ADR-015) + duration. Unit tests cover hit, miss, partial-manifest (no tables), and ADR-015 telemetry safety.
  </goal>

  <context>
